Elevator will be a class
Elevator controller will be a controller class

Elevator will report to controller

Requests will go to controller, which will decide which elevator fulfills task
Buttons pushed in elevator immediately start moving, and send new destination to controller

# of elevators and floors determined by command-line arguments

Elevators have properties:
  # of trips
  current floor
  occupied (how will it know?  Assume that once all dests are set, it's empty?)
  needs maintenance


Elevator Controller has array? obj? of elevators